{"id":167008,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/中国网站数量一年减少41/","date":"2011-07-13T18:00:06Z","modified":"2011-07-16T21:04:43Z","title":"中国网站数量一年减少41%","content":"<p>中国社科院发布了《中国新媒体发展报告(2011)》。报告称，截至2010年底，中国互联网网民数达到4.57亿，手机用户突破8亿户，互联网站总数为191万个，同比2009年减少了132万个，下降幅度达到41%；网页数量达到600亿个，比2009年增长78.6%。报告主要作者刘瑞生说，一些网站是因为受金融危机冲击而关门，还有的网站是因为传播淫秽色情内容被关闭或者被屏蔽。他说，中国一方面在加强内容，另一方面“在管理方面越来越严格，越来越规范”。刘瑞生说，“中国有很高的在线言论自由。最近几年很少仅仅因为控制言论而关闭网站的案例”。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/16a176d7/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%9141%25&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F13%2F1134215%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%9141%25&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F07%2F13%2F1134215%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106217536994/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/16a176d7/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/106217536994/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/16a176d7/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=SMy4c4SfmXw:1OPnaw843Jc:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=SMy4c4SfmXw:1OPnaw843Jc:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动